text: Borgia Norrköping BK is a bandy club in Norrköping, Sweden, established in 1941. The men's bandy team played in the Swedish top division during the season of 1988-1989. == References == ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1941 establishments in Sweden Category:Bandy clubs in Sweden Category:Norrköping
